[normal]We 
[normal]are seeking
[normal] further LMA proposals from communities in Scotland and other parts of the UK
[normal], and have been working
[normal] to raise awareness through media, our own publications and website, and through relevant member organisations such as Development Trust Association Scotland.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]4.6 
[normal]Our programme of LMA publicity includes:
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
