[normal] can be customised to meet the needs/aspirations of
[normal] individual communities. The projects should be led and driven by local organisations, and have broad buy-in from the community. This will help ensure that they are sustainable in the long-term and that they result in genuine devolution of the management o
[normal]f assets.
